{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was skiing by the time I was four.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now I'm afraid of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm afraid to climb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm afraid to jump.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm afraid of getting hurt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure I've been very hurt already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that's what-- that's what's happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's, that's the part of the war that I think often is not even talked about.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because it was such a life-and-death thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was so much about people being murdered on the spot and dying in camps that the more subtle injuries and the more subtle wounds that then continue with you through your life are rarely, rarely talked about.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think there was a film I saw some years ago-- very good Dutch film.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think it was called or something like that that deals with a Dutch boy-- not Jewish, as a matter of fact-- whose family is murdered by the Nazis during the war because they think they're hiding, you know, underground people.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And 30 or 40 years later on a vacation in Italy, he wakes up one morning in a cold sweat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's that sort of thing that continues.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that's why I mentioned that because that's sort of a subtext to what's going on for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we're there--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in-- no, I have no memory of that, no, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The family, again, is the world, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we did it, I think it was done on the QT.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think it's done, you know, it's not like-- obviously, like it was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- I do know my mother continues every night to say prayers with my sister and myself, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By that time, we-- I've learned about the evening prayer, which runs about three, four minutes.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
